.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
node_modules/
dashboard/node_modules/

# Generated agent memory and long-horizon task state. These are created per user.
**/chain/
**/tasks/
# Grown faculties — the per-user Dream Cache (emergent) and promoted faculties (grown).
# Created on first growth; never shipped, so upgrading over an existing install can't
# reset a user's emergent OR promoted faculties.
**/registry/emergent.json
**/registry/grown.json
# Per-user learner state (Phases B-E) — trained operators and covenant-tolerance
# overrides belong to each agent, never to the shipped base. The chain/-rooted
# ledgers (telemetry, salience, replay, dream state) are covered by **/chain/.
**/registry/policy.json
**/registry/scorer.json
**/registry/labeler.json
**/registry/lens/

# Local tooling
.claude/
